::Wolfenstein::

The transwarp portal opens as a small one person vessel comes through it and enters into orbit around Pre-Historic Earth. The ship is clearly Cybertronian in design. As the ship moves light from the sun makes one part visible that was in shawdow. We can see that the ship is marked as a Predacon cruiser. 

In the ship we see that a rather bulked up bot sits in the cockpit. His slick black and blue design is very frightning.(Think of Beast Wars K-9 Maximal toy design but black, blue, and without the animal parts)

Wolfenstein works over the computers, reading information.

&quot;It must have worked, this is Earth, of the past. While many of our ancestors lay in stasis a war rages between Transformers of our time.&quot;

The computer shows the location of Megatron&#39;s Predacon base.

Wolfenstein takes the ship through the atmosphere, and is quick to cloak the ship so he is not picked up by Maximals or worse. 

&quot;I was lucky that i have friends in high places. The Tripredacus Council would have never given me this ship otherwise.&quot;

Now the ship hovors in the air, invisible to all.

&quot;Now I will find out what happaned to my brother...&quot;

Wolfenstein activates a commlink to Megatron&#39;s base.

&quot;This is the Predacon cruiser Warpstar, my name is Wolfenstein. I wish to join your ranks as well as learn of the wherabouts of a soldier under your great command.&quot;

Wolfenstein awaits a response from Megatron or someone at his base.

--Boundary_(ID_5HRwa78b6rMIAu5hitkQTQ)
